Subject: flex problem
Date: Fri, 20 Aug 1993 13:40:56 -0400

I've got a [f]lex-based parser and I'm having trouble grabbing tokens
from yytext: 

(gbd) n 
2220        strcpy(ClassName, yytext); /* move name to the proper place */ 
(gdb) p ClassName 
$1 = 0x21000 "" 
(gdb) p yytext 
$2 = 0x23157 "testobject" 
(gdb) n 
2221        if (toplevel) {                     /* keep this forever if
this is our class */ 
(gdb) p ClassName 
$3 = 0x21000 "W1\002" 
(gdb) p yytext 
$4 = 0x23157 "testobject" 

What's up with this? 

-Gary Keim 
